QUERRY BASED INGESTION - COPY INTO, AUTO LOADER
COPY INTO - INGEST MANUALLY
---
- load large data from cloud storage, directly onto delta tables
- good for static datasets (they dont change frequently) 
e.g. - ingest a folder of parquet files, them create a delta table named *ias_table_parquet_files* - this ingestion was fast and efficient for bulk (the fodler) data
copy into Ias_tabel_parquet_files  from path... fileformat = parquet  format_options=mergeschema=true, copy_options=mergeschema=true


AUTO LOADER - INGEST AUTOMATICALLY
---
- for changind and dynamic datasets
- Auto Loader processes each data file exactly once, and incrementally adds them to the target table.
- auto loader will countinuously monitor a specific cloud storage location ->>if there is new file there, auto loader automatically ingests this new file, when it arrives
e.g. - create table custoemrs_Ias as select * from path... 

